<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA35">
<l>aṭuṅkaṇṭāy veṇmatiyeṉ ṟañci yiruḷpōn</l>
<l>tiṭaṅkoṇ ṭirukkiṉṟa tokkum - paṭaṅko</l>
<l>ḷaṇimiṭaṟṟa pēḻvā yaravacaittāṉ kōla</l>
<l>maṇimiṭaṟṟi ṉuḷḷa maṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fearing “the white moon will kill [us], see”, night comes</l>
<l>[and] is taking as [its] place, it seems, the stain that is</l>
<l>in the beautiful sapphire throat of him who has tied on</l>
<l>the big-mouthed snake, [its] neck adorned by taking a hood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
